    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You momentarily surround a creature you can see within range with electronic interference and holographic illusions. The target must succeed on an Intelligence saving throw, or it takes [[/r 1d6]] lightning damage and moves 5 feet in a random direction if it can move and its speed is at least 5 feet. Roll a [[/r d4]] for the direction: 1, north; 2, south; 3, east; or 4, west. This movement doesn't provoke opportunity attacks, and if the direction rolled is blocked, the target doesn't move.</p>\n<p>The power's damage increases by [[/r 1d6]] when you reach 5th level ([[/r 2d6]]), 11th level ([[/r 3d6]]), and 17th level ([[/r 4d6]]).</p>",
